       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME     PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI94204'.
           05 WS-ULT-DIA-MES       PIC X(02).
           05 WS-SUM-NDIAS         PIC S9(03)V99 COMP-3 VALUE ZEROES.
           05 WS-NUM-DIAS          PIC 9(02)V99.
           05 WS-NUM-DIAS-ANO      PIC 9(03)V99.
           05 WS-NUM-DIAS-APR      PIC 9(03)V99.
           05 WS-NUM-DIAS-TOT      PIC 9(09)V99.
           05 WS-NUM-DIAS-TOL      PIC 9(09)V99.
           05 WS-NUM-DIAS-TOLA     PIC 9(09)V99.
           05 WS-NUM-DIAS-TOLM     PIC 9(09)V99.
           05 WS-FERIADO           PIC X(01).
           05 WS-APROVADO          PIC X(01).
           05 WS-JA-APROVADO       PIC 9(01).
           05 WS-X                 PIC 9(02).
           05 WS-HORAS             PIC S9(8) COMP-3.
           05 WS-QUO               PIC 9(04).
           05 WS-RES               PIC 9(04).
           05 WS-DFERIAS-MIN       PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DFERIAS-MAX       PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DTMESANO          PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DTMESANO.
              10 WS-DTMESANO-ANO   PIC X(04).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-SEP1  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-MES   PIC X(02).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-SEP2  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-DIA   PIC X(02).

           05 WS-DATA-INF          PIC X(10).
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DATA-INF.
              10 WS-DATA-INF-ANO   PIC X(04).
              10 WS-DATA-INF-SEP1  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DATA-INF-MES   PIC X(02).
              10 WS-DATA-INF-SEP2  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DATA-INF-DIA   PIC X(02).

           05 WS-DATA-SUP          PIC X(10).
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DATA-SUP.
              10 WS-DATA-SUP-ANO   PIC X(04).
              10 WS-DATA-SUP-SEP1  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DATA-SUP-MES   PIC X(02).
              10 WS-DATA-SUP-SEP2  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DATA-SUP-DIA   PIC X(02).

           05 WS-ANO-X             PIC X(04).
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-ANO-X.
              10 WS-ANO-9          PIC 9(04).

           05 WS-TABELA-DIAS.
              10 WS-DIAS OCCURS 31 TIMES PIC X.

           05 WS-DDATA-MIN         PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DDATA-MIN.
              10 WS-DDATA-MIN-ANO      PIC X(04).
              10 WS-DDATA-MIN-FILL1    PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DDATA-MIN-MES      PIC X(02).
              10 WS-DDATA-MIN-FILL2    PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DDATA-MIN-DIA      PIC X(02).

           05 WS-DDATA-MAX         PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DDATA-MAX.
              10 WS-DDATA-MAX-ANO      PIC X(04).
              10 WS-DDATA-MAX-FILL1    PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DDATA-MAX-MES      PIC X(02).
              10 WS-DDATA-MAX-FILL2    PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DDATA-MAX-DIA      PIC X(02).

           05 WS-DATA-ULT          PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DATA-ULT.
              10 WS-DATA-ULT-ANO   PIC X(04).
              10 WS-DATA-ULT-SEP1  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DATA-ULT-MES   PIC X(02).
              10 WS-DATA-ULT-SEP2  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DATA-ULT-DIA   PIC X(02).

           05 WS-DATA-VER          PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DATA-VER.
              10 WS-DATA-VER-ANO   PIC X(04).
              10 WS-DATA-VER-SEP1  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DATA-VER-MES   PIC X(02).
              10 WS-DATA-VER-SEP2  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DATA-VER-DIA   PIC X(02).

           05 WS-DATA-GAT          PIC X(20) VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DATA-GAT.
              10 WS-DATA-GAT-ANO   PIC X(10).
              10 WS-DATA-GAT-USER  PIC X(10).
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *              DECLARACOES DE CURSORES DB2                     *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------

           EXEC SQL
            DECLARE CURART01 CURSOR FOR
            SELECT DDATA
                 , CDIASEM
                 , CTIPOFER
            FROM ARVT7001
            WHERE CTIPOFER  = :CON-T
              AND DDATA    >= :WS-DDATA-MIN
              AND DDATA    <= :WS-DDATA-MAX
            ORDER BY DDATA
           END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI94204         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *    CALL 'ARREBENTA'.
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV9420-MSG.
           MOVE COCV9420-ASE               TO COCV9421-ASE.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV9420-ADE               TO COCV9421-ADE.

           PERFORM 2100-VALIDACOES
              THRU 2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-TRATA-DADOS
                 THRU 2200-TRATA-DADOS-EXIT
           END-iF
           .
       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-VALIDACOES.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-VALIDACOES' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *----------------------------------*
      *--- LER COT53_PESSOAS com USER ---*
      *----------------------------------*
      **R  MOVE COCV9421-CUSERID       TO COCD5303-CUTILIZA.
           MOVE COCV9421-CUSERID       TO COCD5303-NTRABALHADOR.
      *
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT NTRABALHADOR
                  , GNOME
                  , CEMPRESA
               INTO :COCD5303-NTRABALHADOR
                  , :COCD5303-GNOME
                  , :COCD5303-CEMPRESA
               FROM COVT5303_PESSOAS
            WHERE NTRABALHADOR = :COCD5303-NTRABALHADOR
            FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT5303               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE 'UTILIZADOR' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCD5303-CUTILIZA'     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (1)
              MOVE  COCD5303-CUTILIZA      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'COCD5303-CEMPRESA'     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (2)
              MOVE  COCD5303-CEMPRESA      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'SQLCODE          '     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (3)
              MOVE  SQLCODE                TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *------------------------------------------------*
      *--- Ler COT54_EMPRESAS de modo a obter CPAIS ---*
      *------------------------------------------------*
           MOVE COCD5303-CEMPRESA      TO COCD5403-CEMPRESA.
      *
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT CEMPRESA
                  , CPAIS
               INTO :COCD5403-CEMPRESA
                  , :COCD5403-CPAIS
               FROM COVT5403_EMPRESAS
            WHERE CEMPRESA = :COCD5403-CEMPRESA
            FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT5403               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE 'EMPRESA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCD5403-CPAIS   '     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (1)
              MOVE  COCD5403-CPAIS         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'COCD5303-CEMPRESA'     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (2)
              MOVE  COCD5303-CEMPRESA      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'SQLCODE          '     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (3)
              MOVE  SQLCODE                TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
      *------------------------------*
      *--- Validar dias dos meses ---*
      *------------------------------*
      *--- Fevereiro
           MOVE COCV9420-CANO TO WS-DATA-VER-ANO.
           MOVE CON-02        TO WS-DATA-VER-MES.
           MOVE CON-01        TO WS-DATA-VER-DIA.
           MOVE CON-SEP       TO WS-DATA-VER-SEP1.
           MOVE CON-SEP       TO WS-DATA-VER-SEP2.
           PERFORM 2180-VER-ULT-DIA
              THRU 2180-VER-ULT-DIA-EXIT.

           IF WS-ULT-DIA-MES = CON-29
              MOVE ZEROS TO WS-RES
           ELSE
              MOVE 1     TO WS-RES
           END-IF

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV9420-CMES     EQUAL CON-02
           AND COCV9420-C31  NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV9421-C31-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INV     TO COCV9421-C31-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV9421-C31-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV9420-CMES     EQUAL CON-02
           AND COCV9420-C30  NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV9421-C30-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INV     TO COCV9421-C30-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV9421-C30-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV9420-CMES     EQUAL CON-02
           AND WS-RES        NOT EQUAL ZEROS
           AND COCV9420-C29  NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV9421-C29-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INV     TO COCV9421-C29-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV9421-C29-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

      *--- Abril
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV9420-CMES     EQUAL CON-04
           AND COCV9420-C31  NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV9421-C31-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INV     TO COCV9421-C31-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV9421-C31-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

      *--- Junho
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV9420-CMES     EQUAL CON-06
           AND COCV9420-C31  NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV9421-C31-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INV     TO COCV9421-C31-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV9421-C31-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

      *--- Setembro
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV9420-CMES     EQUAL CON-09
           AND COCV9420-C31  NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV9421-C31-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INV     TO COCV9421-C31-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV9421-C31-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

      *--- Novembro
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV9420-CMES     EQUAL CON-11
           AND COCV9420-C31  NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV9421-C31-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INV     TO COCV9421-C31-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV9421-C31-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

      *--------------------------------------------------------*
      *--- Validar se marcaram férias em dias feriados      ---*
      *---                                                  ---*
      *--- Validar se marcaram feriados em dias năo feriado ---*
      *--------------------------------------------------------*
           MOVE COCV9420-CANO TO WS-DTMESANO-ANO
           MOVE COCV9420-CMES TO WS-DTMESANO-MES
           MOVE CON-SEP       TO WS-DTMESANO-SEP1
           MOVE CON-SEP       TO WS-DTMESANO-SEP2

      *--- C01
           MOVE CON-01        TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA.
           MOVE WS-DTMESANO   TO ARCD7001-DDATA.
           MOVE CON-NAO       TO WS-FERIADO.
           PERFORM 2500-LER-FERIADOS THRU 2500-LER-FERIADOS-EXIT.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND   WS-FERIADO        EQUAL CON-SIM
           AND ( COCV9420-C01  NOT EQUAL CON-F
           AND   COCV9420-C01  NOT EQUAL CON-T )
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV9421-C01-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INV-FER TO COCV9421-C01-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV9421-C01-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND   WS-FERIADO        EQUAL CON-NAO
           AND ( COCV9420-C01      EQUAL CON-F
            OR   COCV9420-C01      EQUAL CON-T )
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV9421-C01-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INV-NFR TO COCV9421-C01-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV9421-C01-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

      *--- C02
           MOVE CON-02        TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA.
           MOVE WS-DTMESANO   TO ARCD7001-DDATA.
           MOVE CON-NAO       TO WS-FERIADO.
           PERFORM 2500-LER-FERIADOS THRU 2500-LER-FERIADOS-EXIT.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND   WS-FERIADO        EQUAL CON-SIM
           AND ( COCV9420-C02  NOT EQUAL CON-F
           AND   COCV9420-C02  NOT EQUAL CON-T )
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV9421-C02-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INV-FER TO COCV9421-C02-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV9421-C02-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND   WS-FERIADO        EQUAL CON-NAO
           AND ( COCV9420-C02      EQUAL CON-F
            OR   COCV9420-C02      EQUAL CON-T )
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV9421-C02-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INV-NFR TO COCV9421-C02-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV9421-C02-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

      *--- C03
           MOVE CON-03        TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA.
           MOVE WS-DTMESANO   TO ARCD7001-DDATA.
           MOVE CON-NAO       TO WS-FERIADO.
           PERFORM 2500-LER-FERIADOS THRU 2500-LER-FERIADOS-EXIT.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND   WS-FERIADO        EQUAL CON-SIM
           AND ( COCV9420-C03  NOT EQUAL CON-F
           AND   COCV9420-C03  NOT EQUAL CON-T )
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV9421-C03-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INV-FER TO COCV9421-C03-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV9421-C03-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND   WS-FERIADO        EQUAL CON-NAO
           AND ( COCV9420-C03      EQUAL CON-F
            OR   COCV9420-C03      EQUAL CON-T )
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV9421-C03-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INV-NFR TO COCV9421-C03-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV9421-C03-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

      *--- C04
           MOVE CON-04        TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA.
           MOVE WS-DTMESANO   TO ARCD7001-DDATA.
           MOVE CON-NAO       TO WS-FERIADO.
           PERFORM 2500-LER-FERIADOS THRU 2500-LER-FERIADOS-EXIT.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
