           AND WS-APROVADO  EQUAL CON-SIM
           AND COCV9420-C28 EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV9421-C28-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INV-APR TO COCV9421-C28-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV9421-C28-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

      *--- C29
           IF  COCV9421-CMES     = CON-02
           AND WS-RES        NOT = ZEROS
               CONTINUE
           ELSE
               MOVE CON-29        TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
               MOVE WS-DTMESANO   TO COCD7001-DFERIAS
               MOVE CON-NAO       TO WS-APROVADO
               PERFORM 2600-LER-APROVADO THRU 2600-LER-APROVADO-EXIT

               IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
               AND WS-APROVADO  EQUAL CON-SIM
               AND COCV9420-C29 EQUAL SPACES
                   MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                   MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV9421-C29-S
                   MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INV-APR TO COCV9421-C29-MSG
                   MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV9421-C29-CAPLIC
               END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- C30
           IF  COCV9421-CMES     = CON-02
               CONTINUE
           ELSE
               MOVE CON-30        TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
               MOVE WS-DTMESANO   TO COCD7001-DFERIAS
               MOVE CON-NAO       TO WS-APROVADO
               PERFORM 2600-LER-APROVADO THRU 2600-LER-APROVADO-EXIT

               IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
               AND WS-APROVADO  EQUAL CON-SIM
               AND COCV9420-C30 EQUAL SPACES
                   MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                   MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV9421-C30-S
                   MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INV-APR TO COCV9421-C30-MSG
                   MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV9421-C30-CAPLIC
               END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- C31
           IF    COCV9421-CMES     = CON-02
           OR    COCV9421-CMES     = CON-04
           OR    COCV9421-CMES     = CON-06
           OR    COCV9421-CMES     = CON-09
           OR    COCV9421-CMES     = CON-11
               CONTINUE
           ELSE
               MOVE CON-31        TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
               MOVE WS-DTMESANO   TO COCD7001-DFERIAS
               MOVE CON-NAO       TO WS-APROVADO
               PERFORM 2600-LER-APROVADO THRU 2600-LER-APROVADO-EXIT

               IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
               AND WS-APROVADO  EQUAL CON-SIM
               AND COCV9420-C31 EQUAL SPACES
                   MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                   MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV9421-C31-S
                   MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INV-APR TO COCV9421-C31-MSG
                   MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV9421-C31-CAPLIC
               END-IF
           END-IF.

       2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2180-VER-ULT-DIA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2180-VER-ULT-DIA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2180-VER-ULT-DIA ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ZEROS TO WS-ULT-DIA-MES.

           INITIALIZE VIAL1000-AREA-COMUNICACAO
                                   REPLACING  NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                         ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.

           MOVE '09'             TO VIAL1000-COD-PROCESSO.
           MOVE WS-DATA-VER      TO AQCW0005-DTX10
           PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8
              THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8-EXIT
           MOVE AQCW0005-DT98    TO VIAL1000-DAT-INPUT1

           PERFORM VIAP1000-ROTINA-DATAS
              THRU VIAP1000-EXIT.

           IF VIAL1000-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE VIAL1000-DAT-RES-ED TO WS-DATA-ULT
              MOVE WS-DATA-ULT-DIA     TO WS-ULT-DIA-MES
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAL1000-IND-ERROS TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE VIAL1000-COD-ERRO-GRAVE TO
                                     VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
           END-IF.

       2180-VER-ULT-DIA-EXIT.
           EXIT.


      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * LER FERIADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2500-LER-FERIADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2500-LER-FERIADOS  ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.


           MOVE COCD5403-CPAIS TO ARCD7001-CPAIS.

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT DDATA
                 INTO  :ARCD7001-DDATA
                 FROM ARVT7001
                 WHERE CPAIS    = :ARCD7001-CPAIS
                   AND DDATA    = :ARCD7001-DDATA
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-ARVT7001 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 MOVE CON-SIM TO WS-FERIADO
              ELSE
                 MOVE CON-NAO TO WS-FERIADO
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2500-LER-FERIADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * LER APROVADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2600-LER-APROVADO.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2600-LER-APROVADO  ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE CON-A            TO COCD7001-CSITU.
           MOVE COCV9421-CIDEMP  TO COCD7001-CIDEMP.

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT CIDEMP
                      , DFERIAS
                      , CSITU
                 INTO   :COCD7001-CIDEMP
                      , :COCD7001-DFERIAS
                      , :COCD7001-CSITU
                 FROM COVT7001
                 WHERE CIDEMP   = :COCD7001-CIDEMP
                   AND DFERIAS  = :COCD7001-DFERIAS
                   AND CSITU    = :COCD7001-CSITU
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT7001 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 MOVE CON-SIM TO WS-APROVADO
              ELSE
                 MOVE CON-NAO TO WS-APROVADO
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2600-LER-APROVADO-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * 2200-TRATA-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-TRATA-DADOS.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2200-TRATA-DADOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2800-ELIMINA THRU 2800-ELIMINA-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2900-INSERE  THRU 2900-INSERE-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2200-TRATA-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * 2800-ELIMINA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2800-ELIMINA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2800-ELIMINA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *--- Preenche campos da chave lógica de eliminaçăo
           MOVE COCV9421-CIDEMP TO COCD7001-CIDEMP.
           MOVE CON-A           TO COCD7001-CSITU.

           MOVE COCV9420-CANO TO WS-DTMESANO-ANO.
           MOVE COCV9420-CMES TO WS-DTMESANO-MES.
           MOVE CON-SEP       TO WS-DTMESANO-SEP1.
           MOVE CON-SEP       TO WS-DTMESANO-SEP2.
           MOVE CON-01        TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA.
           MOVE WS-DTMESANO   TO WS-DFERIAS-MIN.

           IF COCV9420-CMES = CON-02
              IF WS-RES = ZEROS
                 MOVE CON-29  TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
              ELSE
                 MOVE CON-28  TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
              END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF COCV9420-CMES = CON-04
           OR COCV9420-CMES = CON-06
           OR COCV9420-CMES = CON-09
           OR COCV9420-CMES = CON-11
              MOVE CON-30  TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
           END-IF.

           IF COCV9420-CMES = CON-01
           OR COCV9420-CMES = CON-03
           OR COCV9420-CMES = CON-05
           OR COCV9420-CMES = CON-07
           OR COCV9420-CMES = CON-08
           OR COCV9420-CMES = CON-10
           OR COCV9420-CMES = CON-12
              MOVE CON-31  TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
           END-IF.

           MOVE WS-DTMESANO   TO WS-DFERIAS-MAX.

           EXEC SQL
                 DELETE FROM COVT7001
                 WHERE CIDEMP   = :COCD7001-CIDEMP
                   AND DFERIAS >= :WS-DFERIAS-MIN
                   AND DFERIAS <= :WS-DFERIAS-MAX
                   AND CSITU   <> :COCD7001-CSITU
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT7001 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-NOTFND
              OR DB2-OK
                 CONTINUE
              ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                   TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
              END-IF
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
           END-IF.

       2800-ELIMINA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * 2700-GERA-GATILHO.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2700-GERA-GATILHO.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2700-GERA-GATILHO' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCK0002-GAT-COLAB-FERALT TO COCL0030-CGATILHO.
           MOVE COCD7001-CIDEMP           TO COCL0030-CCHAVE.
           MOVE SPACES                    TO COCL0030-GDESC.
           MOVE COCD7001-DFERIAS          TO WS-DATA-GAT-ANO.
           MOVE COCD7001-CUSERID          TO WS-DATA-GAT-USER.

           MOVE WS-DATA-GAT               TO COCL0030-DADOS.

           PERFORM ETCP0002-FORM-ONLINE-IN
              THRU ETCP0002-FORM-ONLINE-IN-EXIT.

           PERFORM COCP0030-CALL-ROTINA
              THRU COCP0030-CALL-ROTINA-EXIT.

           PERFORM ETCP0002-STD-END
              THRU ETCP0002-STD-END-EXIT.

       2700-GERA-GATILHO-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * 2900-INSERE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2900-INSERE.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2900-INSERE ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *--- Retira do écran e coloca na tabela
           MOVE COCV9421-C01 TO WS-DIAS(01).
           MOVE COCV9421-C02 TO WS-DIAS(02).
           MOVE COCV9421-C03 TO WS-DIAS(03).
           MOVE COCV9421-C04 TO WS-DIAS(04).
           MOVE COCV9421-C05 TO WS-DIAS(05).
           MOVE COCV9421-C06 TO WS-DIAS(06).
           MOVE COCV9421-C07 TO WS-DIAS(07).
           MOVE COCV9421-C08 TO WS-DIAS(08).
           MOVE COCV9421-C09 TO WS-DIAS(09).
           MOVE COCV9421-C10 TO WS-DIAS(10).
           MOVE COCV9421-C11 TO WS-DIAS(11).
           MOVE COCV9421-C12 TO WS-DIAS(12).
           MOVE COCV9421-C13 TO WS-DIAS(13).
           MOVE COCV9421-C14 TO WS-DIAS(14).
           MOVE COCV9421-C15 TO WS-DIAS(15).
           MOVE COCV9421-C16 TO WS-DIAS(16).
           MOVE COCV9421-C17 TO WS-DIAS(17).
           MOVE COCV9421-C18 TO WS-DIAS(18).
           MOVE COCV9421-C19 TO WS-DIAS(19).
           MOVE COCV9421-C20 TO WS-DIAS(20).
           MOVE COCV9421-C21 TO WS-DIAS(21).
           MOVE COCV9421-C22 TO WS-DIAS(22).
           MOVE COCV9421-C23 TO WS-DIAS(23).
           MOVE COCV9421-C24 TO WS-DIAS(24).
           MOVE COCV9421-C25 TO WS-DIAS(25).
           MOVE COCV9421-C26 TO WS-DIAS(26).
           MOVE COCV9421-C27 TO WS-DIAS(27).
           MOVE COCV9421-C28 TO WS-DIAS(28).
           MOVE COCV9421-C29 TO WS-DIAS(29).
           MOVE COCV9421-C30 TO WS-DIAS(30).
           MOVE COCV9421-C31 TO WS-DIAS(31).
      *--- Cria registo para todos os que sejam 8 ou 4
           MOVE 1 TO WS-X.
           MOVE ZEROS TO WS-NUM-DIAS.
           PERFORM UNTIL WS-X > 31
                   IF WS-DIAS(WS-X) = CON-8
                   OR WS-DIAS(WS-X) = CON-4
      *-------------- Conta dias deste Ano / Męs
                      IF WS-DIAS(WS-X) = CON-8
                         COMPUTE WS-NUM-DIAS = WS-NUM-DIAS + 1
                      END-IF

                      IF WS-DIAS(WS-X) = CON-4
                         COMPUTE WS-NUM-DIAS = WS-NUM-DIAS + 0.5
                      END-IF
                      MOVE WS-NUM-DIAS TO COCV9421-NUMDIAS
      *-------------- Ver se já existe férias aprovadas para este dia
                      MOVE COCV9421-CIDEMP  TO COCD7001-CIDEMP
                      MOVE COCV9421-CANO    TO WS-DTMESANO-ANO
                      MOVE COCV9421-CMES    TO WS-DTMESANO-MES
                      MOVE CON-SEP          TO WS-DTMESANO-SEP1
                      MOVE CON-SEP          TO WS-DTMESANO-SEP2
                      MOVE WS-X             TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
                      MOVE WS-DTMESANO      TO COCD7001-DFERIAS
                      MOVE CON-A            TO COCD7001-CSITU

                      IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS

                         EXEC SQL
                          SELECT CIDEMP, DFERIAS, CSITU
                          INTO  :COCD7001-CIDEMP
                             ,  :COCD7001-DFERIAS
                             ,  :COCD7001-CSITU
                          FROM COVT7001
                          WHERE CIDEMP   = :COCD7001-CIDEMP
                            AND DFERIAS  = :COCD7001-DFERIAS
                            AND CSITU    = :COCD7001-CSITU
                         END-EXEC

                         MOVE CON-COVT7001 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

                         PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
                            THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

                         IF DB2-OK
                            MOVE 1 TO WS-JA-APROVADO
                         ELSE
                            MOVE ZEROS TO WS-JA-APROVADO
                         END-IF
                      END-IF

                      IF WS-JA-APROVADO = ZEROS
      *-------------- Cria registo
                       MOVE COCV9421-CIDEMP  TO COCD7001-CIDEMP
                       MOVE COCV9421-CANO    TO WS-DTMESANO-ANO
                       MOVE COCV9421-CMES    TO WS-DTMESANO-MES
                       MOVE CON-SEP          TO WS-DTMESANO-SEP1
                       MOVE CON-SEP          TO WS-DTMESANO-SEP2
                       MOVE WS-X             TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
                       MOVE WS-DTMESANO      TO COCD7001-DFERIAS
                       IF WS-DIAS(WS-X) = CON-8
                          MOVE CON-8-9       TO COCD7001-ZHORAS
                       ELSE
                          MOVE CON-4-9       TO COCD7001-ZHORAS
                       END-IF
                       MOVE CON-N            TO COCD7001-CSITU
                       MOVE COCV9421-CUSERID TO COCD7001-CUSERID
                       MOVE SPACES           TO COCD7001-CUSERAPR
                       MOVE CON-DATA-MIN     TO COCD7001-DDTAPR

                       IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                          PERFORM 2950-ESCREVE-REG
                             THRU 2950-ESCREVE-REG-EXIT
                       END-IF
                      END-IF
                   END-IF
                   ADD 1 TO WS-X
           END-PERFORM.

      *--- Preenche campos acumulados dias ferias Ano e
      *--- dias ferias Ano aprovados
           PERFORM 2960-CALCULA-ACM
              THRU 2960-CALCULA-ACM-EXIT.

       2900-INSERE-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * 2950-ESCREVE-REG
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2950-ESCREVE-REG.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2950-ESCREVE-REG   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
            INSERT INTO COVT7001
            (  CIDEMP
             , DFERIAS
             , ZHORAS
             , CSITU
             , CUSERAPR
             , DDTAPR
             , CUSERID
             , HTIMEST   )
            VALUES
            (  :COCD7001-CIDEMP
             , :COCD7001-DFERIAS
             , :COCD7001-ZHORAS
             , :COCD7001-CSITU
             , :COCD7001-CUSERAPR
             , :COCD7001-DDTAPR
             , :COCD7001-CUSERID
             , CURRENT TIMESTAMP  )
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT7001 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF DB2-DUPREC
           OR DB2-OK
              IF DB2-OK
                 PERFORM 2700-GERA-GATILHO
                    THRU 2700-GERA-GATILHO-EXIT
              END-IF
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
           END-IF.

       2950-ESCREVE-REG-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * 2960-CALCULA-ACM
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2960-CALCULA-ACM.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2960-CALCULA-ACM   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Obtém crédito de férias
      *--- Obtém Total de dias de férias de todos os anos
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2121-CREDITOS
                 THRU 2121-CREDITOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Preenche campos acumulados dias ferias Ano e
      *--- dias ferias Ano aprovados
           MOVE ZEROS             TO WS-NUM-DIAS-ANO.
           MOVE ZEROS             TO WS-NUM-DIAS-APR.
           MOVE COCV9420-CIDEMP   TO COCD7001-CIDEMP.
           MOVE COCV9420-CANO     TO WS-DATA-INF-ANO.
           MOVE CON-01            TO WS-DATA-INF-MES.
           MOVE CON-01            TO WS-DATA-INF-DIA.
           MOVE CON-SEP           TO WS-DATA-INF-SEP1.
           MOVE CON-SEP           TO WS-DATA-INF-SEP2.
           MOVE COCV9420-CANO     TO WS-DATA-SUP-ANO.
           MOVE CON-12            TO WS-DATA-SUP-MES.
           MOVE CON-31            TO WS-DATA-SUP-DIA.
           MOVE CON-SEP           TO WS-DATA-SUP-SEP1.
           MOVE CON-SEP           TO WS-DATA-SUP-SEP2.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT CIDEMP, IFNULL(SUM(ZHORAS), 0)
                 INTO  :COCD7001-CIDEMP
                    ,  :WS-HORAS
                 FROM COVT7001
                 WHERE CIDEMP   = :COCD7001-CIDEMP
                 AND   DFERIAS >= :WS-DATA-INF
                 AND   DFERIAS <= :WS-DATA-SUP
                 GROUP BY CIDEMP
                 ORDER BY CIDEMP
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT7001
             TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 COMPUTE WS-NUM-DIAS-ANO = WS-HORAS / 8
                 MOVE WS-NUM-DIAS-ANO TO COCV9421-NUMDIASANO
              END-IF
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT CIDEMP, IFNULL(SUM(ZHORAS), 0)
                 INTO  :COCD7001-CIDEMP
                    ,  :WS-HORAS
                 FROM COVT7001
                 WHERE CIDEMP   = :COCD7001-CIDEMP
                 AND   DFERIAS >= :WS-DATA-INF
                 AND   DFERIAS <= :WS-DATA-SUP
                 AND   CSITU    = :CON-A
                 GROUP BY CIDEMP
                 ORDER BY CIDEMP
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT7001
             TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 COMPUTE WS-NUM-DIAS-APR = WS-HORAS / 8
                 MOVE WS-NUM-DIAS-APR TO COCV9421-NUMDIASAPR
              END-IF
           END-IF.

      *    COMPUTE COCV9421-NUMDIASANO = COCV9421-NUMDIASANO -
      *                                  WS-NUM-DIAS-TOL.
      *    COMPUTE COCV9421-NUMDIASAPR = COCV9421-NUMDIASAPR -
      *                                  WS-NUM-DIAS-TOLA.

       2960-CALCULA-ACM-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2121-CREDITOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2121-CREDITOS.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2121-CREDITOS      ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Obtém crédito de férias
           MOVE COCV9420-CIDEMP   TO COCD7100-CIDEMP.
           MOVE COCV9420-CANO     TO COCD7100-CANO.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT IFNULL(SUM(NDIAS), 0)
                 INTO
                       :WS-SUM-NDIAS
                 FROM COVT7100
                 WHERE CIDEMP   = :COCD7100-CIDEMP
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT7100
             TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 CONTINUE
              ELSE
                 MOVE ZEROS TO WS-SUM-NDIAS
              END-IF
           END-IF.


      *--- Obtem todos os dias de férias de todos os anos
           MOVE ZEROS             TO WS-NUM-DIAS-TOT.
           MOVE COCV9420-CIDEMP   TO COCD7001-CIDEMP.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT CIDEMP, IFNULL(SUM(ZHORAS), 0)
                 INTO  :COCD7001-CIDEMP
                    ,  :WS-HORAS
                 FROM COVT7001
                 WHERE CIDEMP   = :COCD7001-CIDEMP
                 GROUP BY CIDEMP
                 ORDER BY CIDEMP
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT7001
             TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 COMPUTE WS-NUM-DIAS-TOT = WS-HORAS / 8
              END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Ver se existe algum dia de férias marcado numa tolerância.
      *--- Se existir, năo conta como férias, somando ao saldo.
           MOVE ZEROS             TO WS-NUM-DIAS-TOL.
           MOVE ZEROS             TO WS-NUM-DIAS-TOLA.
           MOVE ZEROS             TO WS-NUM-DIAS-TOLM.

           PERFORM 2125-VERIFICA-TOL
              THRU 2125-VERIFICA-TOL-EXIT.

      *--- Preenche campo saldo de férias
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *       COMPUTE WS-NUM-DIAS-TOL = WS-NUM-DIAS-TOLA +
      *                                 WS-NUM-DIAS-TOLM
      *       COMPUTE COCV9421-SALDOFER = COCD7100-NDIAS
      *                                 - WS-NUM-DIAS-TOT
      *                                 + WS-NUM-DIAS-TOL
              COMPUTE COCV9421-SALDOFER = WS-SUM-NDIAS
                                        - WS-NUM-DIAS-TOT
           END-IF.

       2121-CREDITOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.


      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2125-VERIFICA-TOL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2125-VERIFICA-TOL.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2125-VERIFICA-TOL' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2026-OPEN
                 THRU 2026-OPEN-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2027-FETCH
                 THRU 2027-FETCH-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF DB2-OK
                PERFORM 2028-CONTINUA
                   THRU 2028-CONTINUA-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2029-CLOSE
              THRU 2029-CLOSE-EXIT.

       2125-VERIFICA-TOL-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2026-OPEN
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2026-OPEN.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2026-OPEN' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE COCV9420-CANO       TO WS-DDATA-MIN-ANO.
           MOVE CON-SEP             TO WS-DDATA-MIN-FILL1.
           MOVE CON-01              TO WS-DDATA-MIN-MES.
           MOVE CON-SEP             TO WS-DDATA-MIN-FILL2.
           MOVE CON-01              TO WS-DDATA-MIN-DIA.

           MOVE COCV9420-CANO       TO WS-DDATA-MAX-ANO.
           MOVE CON-SEP             TO WS-DDATA-MAX-FILL1.
           MOVE CON-12              TO WS-DDATA-MAX-MES.
           MOVE CON-SEP             TO WS-DDATA-MAX-FILL2.
           MOVE CON-31              TO WS-DDATA-MAX-DIA.

           EXEC SQL
             OPEN CURART01
           END-EXEC.
      *
           MOVE CON-ARVT7001               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
       2026-OPEN-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2027-FETCH
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2027-FETCH.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2027-FETCH' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           EXEC SQL
              FETCH CURART01
              INTO  :ARCD7001-DDATA
                  , :ARCD7001-CDIASEM
                  , :ARCD7001-CTIPOFER
           END-EXEC.
      *
           MOVE CON-COVT7001               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
       2027-FETCH-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                       2028-CONTINUA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2028-CONTINUA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2028-CONTINUA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           PERFORM 2030-TRATA-OCCURS
              THRU 2030-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT
             UNTIL NOT DB2-OK
                OR NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS.
      *
       2028-CONTINUA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2030-TRATA-OCCURS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2030-TRATA-OCCURS.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
             MOVE '2030-TRATA-OCCURS'          TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
             PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Verifica se existe registo no COT70 para o mesmo dia da
      *--- tolerancia que foi lida no ART70.
           MOVE COCV9420-CIDEMP   TO COCD7001-CIDEMP.
           MOVE ARCD7001-DDATA    TO COCD7001-DFERIAS.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT CIDEMP
                     , DFERIAS
                     , CSITU
                 INTO  :COCD7001-CIDEMP
                    ,  :COCD7001-DFERIAS
                    ,  :COCD7001-CSITU
                 FROM COVT7001
                 WHERE CIDEMP   = :COCD7001-CIDEMP
                   AND DFERIAS  = :COCD7001-DFERIAS
                 FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT7001
             TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 IF COCD7001-CSITU = CON-APROVADAS
                   COMPUTE WS-NUM-DIAS-TOLA = WS-NUM-DIAS-TOLA + 1
                 ELSE
                   COMPUTE WS-NUM-DIAS-TOLM = WS-NUM-DIAS-TOLM + 1
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             PERFORM 2027-FETCH
                THRU 2027-FETCH-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
       2030-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2029-CLOSE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2029-CLOSE.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2029-CLOSE' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           EXEC SQL
               CLOSE CURART01
           END-EXEC.
      *
       2029-CLOSE-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV9421-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV9421-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV9421-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.


       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP1000.
           COPY VIATP300.
           COPY VIAP0010.
           COPY VIAP0016.
           COPY TGCP2000.
           COPY EXCP0200.
           COPY AQCP0005.
           COPY ETCP0002.
           COPY COCP0030.
